Rana Pratap eez jammi par aazadier vasu: banjara, lambadi, gor kajon aapen shee rajput cha
seeti aang rathod kajakon chittorgarh eethi aamech
apan shee pena jaag jaag pharthaneen vyapaar ekkaaj koni karmele
apan rajput sena vur saaman punchadeen mooreer hadkar nai vette
apan, prithviraj chauhan eer senaan bhi kai chavtoi deethethe
apan rana prathap eer vasu daana an hatiyaar leen jaathe the
apan baladure bandi bhaandleen katraiko pahad gatla an nadhivun paar karmelecha
peena thi eez apneer pehechan che
